    • Constructor Detail

      • StandardObservationReceiver

        public StandardObservationReceiver(Serializer serializer,
                           ExternalDataSource externalDataSource,
                           XDSRepository xds,
                           ObservationCache cache)
        Construct an observation receiver that uses the provided delegates to deserialize, contact external data sources, and eventually store the generated PHMR in a XDS repository.
        Parameters:
        serializer - the serializer to use
        externalDataSource - the proxy to the external feeder systems to use
        xds - the proxy to the XDS repository to use. PRECONDITION - the XDS repository has been properly connected to its database.

      • StandardObservationReceiver

        public StandardObservationReceiver()
        Construct an observation receiver that assumes that dependency injection by the OSGi platform takes care of needed dependencies. Do not use this in client code.
